org.franca.core.franca

Interface FMethod

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FMethodImpl

    public interface FMethod
extends FModelElement
    A representation of the model object 'FMethod'. The definition of a Franca method as part of an FInterface. Methods without out arguments might have be flagged as 'fireAndForget'. See the Franca IDL chapter in the Franca User Guide for very detailed information on method semantics.

    The following features are supported:

    • Fire And Forget
    • In Args
    • Out Args
    • Error Enum
    • Errors
    • Selector
    • Error Comment

    See Also:
    FrancaPackage.getFMethod()
